    - emit {"door": "one-way"|"two-way", "reasons": [...], "confidence": 0-10}
    - exit 0 always; the confirm flow is a separate, interactive concern

This stub deliberately does not implement the confirm flow (that is a non-goal this
sprint, alongside the secrets-tier interactive confirms).
"""

